snippet.title: ROCHE LIMIT: The Death of CMK | PowerPoint Game | Trailer #1 [Release V1.2 Link in Description]
snippet.description:
Follow the link below to download the game!
(With more endings coming soon!)
PowerPoint 2016 or newer is highly recommended 
https://www.mediafire.com/file/n1gs23agwb7wl2q/ROCHE_LIMIT_%255BPre-Release_V2.2%255D.zip/file

As of this release, the game has a single ending with a variety of different minor variations to discover. So stay tuned for the updated version with additional endings!

This is the first teaser trailer from the upcoming PowerPoint horror game "Roche Limit: The Death of CMK". More preview content coming soon.

Follow the game's Instagram account:
https://www.instagram.com/roche_limit_official

Check out my previous game The EdCo Incident: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLhlogqdchUL61JrfTgcl0s2YoIgD2GclV
